Subject: [PATCH net 3/3] bnxt_en: Reset PTP tx_avail after possible firmware reset
Date: Fri,  5 Apr 2024 16:55:13 -0700
Message-Id: <20240405235513.64668-4-michael.chan@broadcom.com>
